{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/gatsby-markdown-image-decoration/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"NARAZUKE","author":[{"name":"nozzle","summary":"who lives in gummaken.","social":{"github":"nozzlex3"}},{"name":"konnyaku","summary":"who is known as Siege Sukosuko Samurai.","social":{"github":"wabetarou"}}]}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"ba945092-0ec3-5e3e-bbfe-136edb5a2513","excerpt":"経緯 CSS がコンフリクトした\n 理由 markdown に画像をアップロードしても自由にクラスを指定できず細かい設定ができない!!! 引用元:gatsby の image について 解決策 CSS の部分文字セレクタを使って alt 属性の部分一致を使う。 解説  : foo 属性の bar 前方一致  : foo…","html":"<h2>経緯</h2>\n<p>CSS がコンフリクトした\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; overflow: visible\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/93045bd9552d93d388473a85c7797b6d/2c288/blog-image_02.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 118.9873417721519%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"blog image 02\"\n        title=\"blog image 02\"\n        src=\"/static/93045bd9552d93d388473a85c7797b6d/f058b/blog-image_02.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/93045bd9552d93d388473a85c7797b6d/c26ae/blog-image_02.png 158w,\n/static/93045bd9552d93d388473a85c7797b6d/6bdcf/blog-image_02.png 315w,\n/static/93045bd9552d93d388473a85c7797b6d/f058b/blog-image_02.png 630w,\n/static/93045bd9552d93d388473a85c7797b6d/2c288/blog-image_02.png 684w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>理由</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>markdown に画像をアップロードしても自由にクラスを指定できず細かい設定ができない!!!</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>引用元:<a href=\"https://narazuke.github.io/gatsby_image/\">gatsby の image について</a></p>\n<h2>解決策</h2>\n<p>CSS の部分文字セレクタを使って alt 属性の部分一致を使う。</p>\n<h2>解説</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">[foo^=&quot;bar&quot;]{}</code> : foo 属性の bar 前方一致</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">[foo$=&quot;bar&quot;]{}</code> : foo 属性の bar 後方一致</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">[foo*=&quot;bar&quot;]{}</code> : foo 属性の bar 部分一致</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>使用例</h2>\n<h3>基本</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token operator\">!</span>[<span class=\"token content\">lenna</span>](<span class=\"token url\">lenna.jpg</span>)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 512px; overflow: visible\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/aa84bc36cfd33497d494427e7f231f1f/36dd4/lenna.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 93.67088607594937%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"lenna\"\n        title=\"lenna\"\n        src=\"/static/aa84bc36cfd33497d494427e7f231f1f/36dd4/lenna.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/aa84bc36cfd33497d494427e7f231f1f/ff44c/lenna.jpg 158w,\n/static/aa84bc36cfd33497d494427e7f231f1f/a6688/lenna.jpg 315w,\n/static/aa84bc36cfd33497d494427e7f231f1f/36dd4/lenna.jpg 512w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>反転</h3>\n<p>src/style.css に、alt 属性に<code class=\"language-text\">--reverse</code>が含まれると反転する CSS を書く。<br>\nimg と[]の間に空白があると失敗します。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title\">src/style.css</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* alt属性に--reverseを含むと左右反転する */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">img[alt*=\"--reverse\"]</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">scale</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>-1<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 1<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token operator\">!</span>[<span class=\"token content\">lenna --reverse</span>](<span class=\"token url\">lenna.jpg</span>)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 512px; overflow: visible\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/aa84bc36cfd33497d494427e7f231f1f/36dd4/lenna.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 93.67088607594937%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"lenna --reverse\"\n        title=\"lenna --reverse\"\n        src=\"/static/aa84bc36cfd33497d494427e7f231f1f/36dd4/lenna.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/aa84bc36cfd33497d494427e7f231f1f/ff44c/lenna.jpg 158w,\n/static/aa84bc36cfd33497d494427e7f231f1f/a6688/lenna.jpg 315w,\n/static/aa84bc36cfd33497d494427e7f231f1f/36dd4/lenna.jpg 512w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>反転できている。</p>\n<h3>パディング</h3>\n<p>src/style.css に、alt 属性に<code class=\"language-text\">--my-padding</code> を含むと padding を設ける CSS を書く</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* alt属性に--my-paddingを含むと上下に10%, 左右に25%の空白を作る */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">img[alt*=\"--my-padding\"]</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10% 25%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token operator\">!</span>[<span class=\"token content\">lenna --my-padding</span>](<span class=\"token url\">lenna.jpg</span>)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 512px; overflow: visible\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/aa84bc36cfd33497d494427e7f231f1f/36dd4/lenna.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 93.67088607594937%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"lenna --my-padding\"\n        title=\"lenna --my-padding\"\n        src=\"/static/aa84bc36cfd33497d494427e7f231f1f/36dd4/lenna.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/aa84bc36cfd33497d494427e7f231f1f/ff44c/lenna.jpg 158w,\n/static/aa84bc36cfd33497d494427e7f231f1f/a6688/lenna.jpg 315w,\n/static/aa84bc36cfd33497d494427e7f231f1f/36dd4/lenna.jpg 512w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>できている。<br>\nこのページを再読み込みしてほしい。padding した領域に一瞬ブラーの残像が表示されるのが分かると思う。\ngatsby-image の blur-up で読込中にブラーを表示する設定にしているためである。この時表示される base64 の画像には CSS が適用されないため、このような表示になってしまう。</p>\n<h3>マージン</h3>\n<p>src/style.css に、alt 属性に<code class=\"language-text\">--my-margin</code> を含むと margin を設ける CSS を書く<br>\n通常の場合 gatsby-image の CSS が優先されてしまうため、CSS に<code class=\"language-text\">!important</code>をつけて、style.css を優先させる。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* alt属性に--my-marginを含むと上下左右15%の空白を作る */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">img[alt*=\"--my-margin\"]</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 15% <span class=\"token important\">!important</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token operator\">!</span>[<span class=\"token content\">lenna --my-margin</span>](<span class=\"token url\">lenna.jpg</span>)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 512px; overflow: visible\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/aa84bc36cfd33497d494427e7f231f1f/36dd4/lenna.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 93.67088607594937%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"lenna --my-margin\"\n        title=\"lenna --my-margin\"\n        src=\"/static/aa84bc36cfd33497d494427e7f231f1f/36dd4/lenna.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/aa84bc36cfd33497d494427e7f231f1f/ff44c/lenna.jpg 158w,\n/static/aa84bc36cfd33497d494427e7f231f1f/a6688/lenna.jpg 315w,\n/static/aa84bc36cfd33497d494427e7f231f1f/36dd4/lenna.jpg 512w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n…<br>\n…<br>\n…<br>\n…<br>\nblur-up の画像がずれて、読み込み中とは思えないおかしな挙動に見える。</p>\n<h2>まとめ</h2>\n<p>alt 属性を利用した Markdown の画像への CSS の適用法は、個々の記事ですこしだけ装飾したい時などに便利である。 もしこの方法で padding や margin を作るときは、blur-up の設定は削除したほうが良いかもしれない。</p>","fields":{"slug":"/gatsby-markdown-image-decoration/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"gatsbyの特定のimgにCSSを適用","created":"2021-2-10 Wed","updated":"2021-2-11 Thu","description":"CSSの部分文字セレクタを使って、Markdownの特定の画像を装飾する","tag":["css"],"author":["nozzle"],"index":"18"}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/linux-command-filesystem/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Linuxのファイルシステムコマンドまとめ"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/favorite-book/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"好きな本"}}},"pageContext":{"index":18,"id":"ba945092-0ec3-5e3e-bbfe-136edb5a2513","previousPostId":"eae4dd2d-189f-5ad8-aaa8-8cd71e6ee638","nextPostId":"3f8d52d7-671a-59d0-a70a-ebce6be088c1"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3284037645","500847697"]}